<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Purchase Confirmation</title>
    <style>

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .username {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0066cc;
        }
        .activation-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ff6600;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Hello, <span class="username"><%= user.name %></span>!</h1>
    <p>Thank you for purchasing the course.</p>
    <p>Your activation code is: <span class="activation-code"><%= activationCode%></span></p>
    <p>This code is valid for the next 5 minutes.</p>
    <p>Enjoy your learning experience!</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
